\fs20\cgrid {\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 Nh\'f7ng m\'d1o v\'c6t y h\'e4c theo ki\'d3u d\'a9n gian Ph\'ad\'acng T\'a9y
\par }\pard \qj\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 Trong cu\'e9c s\'e8ng ch\'f3ng ta th\'ad\'eang g\'c6p nh\'f7ng r\'bec r\'e8i g\'a9y kh\'e3 ch\'deu. Song ch\'d8 c\'c7n bi\'d5t m\'e9t s\'e8 m\'d1o v\'c6t d\'d4 l\'b5m, b\'b9n s\'cf xo\'b8 b\'e1 \'ae
\'ad\'eec nh\'f7ng kh\'e3 ch\'deu \'cay.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 1. M\'bet c\'e3 n\'e4ng ph\'dda d\'ad\'edi ( b\'e4ng m\'bet):}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  D\'efng hai b\'dech tr\'b5 lipton nh\'f3ng v\'b5o n\'ad\'edc \'cam, n\'bbm xu\'e8ng gi\'ad\'eang v\'b5 \'ae\'c6t l\'aan ch\'e7 n\'e4ng \'eb m\'be
t
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 2. S\'e8t l\'b9nh:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  \'a1n x\'f3p g\'b5 g\'e5m th\'det g\'b5 quay n\'cau v\'edi 3 c\'a9y c\'c7n t\'a9y, 2 l\'b8 nguy\'d6t qu\'d5 , m\'e9t c\'f1 h\'b5nh t\'a9y v\'b5 mu\'e8i. Bu\'e6i t\'e8i nh\'cap m\'e9t t\'b8
ch n\'ad\'edc \'cam c\'e3 pha m\'e9t mu\'e7ng n\'ad\'edc c\'e8t chanh, m\'e9t l\'b8t t\'e1i c\'bet nh\'e1, ti\'aau v\'b5 b\'e9t vitamine C
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 3. T\'b8o b\'e3n:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  C\'bet 6 th\'a9n c\'a9y \'ae\'dea ho\'b5ng th\'b5nh mi\'d5ng d\'b5i 5 cm, n\'cau tr\'aan l\'f6a liu riu v\'edi n\'ad\'edc x\'a9m x\'cap t\'f5 10 \'ae\'d5n 15 ph\'f3t cho \'ae\'d5n khi m\'d2
m. N\'d5u mu\'e8n, b\'b9n c\'e3 th\'d3 th\'aam m\'e9t t\'b8ch r\'ad\'eci tr\'b8i d\'a9u l\'b9nh trong khi l\'f6a \'aeang s\'abi.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 4. Nh\'f8c \'ae\'c7u:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  \'a7\'bep kh\'a8n n\'e3ng ph\'dda sau c\'e6, kh\'a8n l\'b9nh \'eb tr\'b8n. N\'bbm xu\'e8ng, nh\'bem m\'bet v\'b5 t\'ad\'ebng t\'ad\'eeng s\'e3ng bi\'d3n \'aeang l\'a8n t\'a8n.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 5. C\'b6m th\'cay kh\'e3 ch\'deu khi c\'e3 kinh:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  N\'cau s\'abi m\'e9t t\'b8ch n\'ad\'edc v\'edi g\'f5ng nghi\'d2n cho m\'e9t b\'dech tr\'b5 lipton v\'b5o v\'b5 u\'e8ng ch\'c7m ch\'cbm.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 6. N\'cac c\'f4c : 
\par }{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 - \'a7\'d3 m\'e9t t\'ea gi\'cay m\'b5u s\'c9m l\'aan m\'f2i mi\'d6ng v\'b5 th\'eb b\'d7nh th\'ad\'eang.
\par - \'a7\'d3 chi\'d5c mu\'e7ng kim lo\'b9i v\'b5o ly n\'ad\'edc v\'b5 u\'e8ng.
\par - \'d0p chi\'d5c mu\'e7ng l\'aan th\'b8i d\'ad\'acng.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 7. Nh\'e4t:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  \'a7\'bep c\'b5 r\'e8t n\'cau nh\'f5 hay b\'e9t nh\'b7o c\'e3 t\'e1i s\'e8ng nghi\'d2n.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 8. Vi\'aam h\'e4ng:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  
\par - Nu\'e8t m\'e9t mu\'e7ng m\'cbt ong
\par - Nh\'cap m\'e9t ly n\'ad\'edc t\'b8o m\'e7i ng\'b5y 2 gi\'ea;
\par - Ho\'b5 tan m\'e9t mu\'e7ng mu\'e8i trong ly n\'ad\'edc \'cam r\'e5i s\'f3c mi\'d6ng m\'e7i gi\'ea.
\par }{\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 9. D\'c7u b\'c7m xanh \'aeen:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  Nghi\'d2n n\'b8t khoai t\'a9y s\'e8ng r\'e5i \'ae\'bep l\'aan v\'d5t b\'c7m, c\'e9t h\'ea l\'edp v\'b6i b\'aan ngo\'b5i, \'ae\'d3 y\'aan 2-3 gi\'ea.
\par }\pard \qj\nowidctlpar\tx1134\tx2268\tx3402\tx4536\tx5670\tx6804\tx7938\tx9072\tx10206\tx11340\tx12474\tx13608\tx14742\tx15876\adjustright {\b\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0 10. R\'b8t da:}{\f17\fs26\cf9\cgrid0  Tr\'e9n m\'cbt v\'b5 t\'b8o \'ae\'cbp n\'b8t v\'edi t
\'fb l\'d6 b\'bbng nhau r\'e5i \'ae\'bep l\'aan ch\'e7 r\'b8t.}{
